msgid "\\item Mindful Check-In; \\item Mindfulness of Emotions (with \\emph{Guest House} Reading)."
msgstr ""

#: en/mbrpra-sessions.tex:69
msgid "At random times, pause and mindfully check-in. Notice any emotions you might be feeling with a sense of openness and acceptance."
msgstr ""

#: en/mbrpra-sessions.tex:70
