msgid "Audio-guided exercises"
msgstr ""

#: en/mbrpra-start.tex:76
msgid "Mindful Check-in"
msgstr ""

#: en/mbrpra-start.tex:77
msgid "Body Scan"
msgstr ""

#: en/mbrpra-start.tex:77
msgid "Check-in with yourself. Notice what’s going on in your body and mind. Then, focus your attention on your breathing. \\par The Mindful Check-in is a core exercise in this program that we practice at the beginning of every session. This a good practice to listen to on a regular basis.Of course, mix it up too and listen to other exercises, such as the one’s below."
msgstr ""

#: en/mbrpra-start.tex:78
msgid "“Scan” your body and bring a curious awareness to sensations you notice."
msgstr ""

